data.description: Bring your large family home to this exceptional 4 Bedroom 3 1/2 Bath  corner lot house located in the desirable Sedona Subdivision. This  property boasts 10 Ft ceilings with 3 bedrooms and two full baths  located upstairs as well as a large game room and covered balcony  overlooking the Heritage Oaks Park and its 100-year-old oak trees  providing a canopy of shade to such amenities as a gravel walking  trail, newly installed basketball court and large playground offering  endless opportunities for outdoor fun and exercise.    The large master bedroom is conveniently located downstairs with a  walk-in closet. dual vanity sinks and an oversized bathtub. In the  Kitchen you will enjoy ample granite counter space, stainless steel  appliances an open layout to the living room with a gas fireplace and  walls large enough to hold an 85"+ TV.  Downstairs also includes a  large open dining room which could also be used as an office.    Quickly you will see how this home has been set up for efficiency and  entertainment as you step out into the massive backyard patio  surrounded by beautiful oak trees perfect for family gatherings! Also  included are two sheds, a full walkway from the backyard to the front  yard and conveniently located gates on both sides of the house. The  front yard offers plenty of shade provided by the numerous mature oak  trees as well as an additional covered patio and oversized driveway  large enough to park 3 vehicles!    The neighborhood homeowners association includes an abundance of  amenities to enjoy such as a large resort style pool, large pavilion,  fishing pond, miles of hiking and biking trails and picturesque park  with outdoor amphitheater.    Besides the superb location to Randolph AFB, Schertz Parks, Cibolo  Main Street, multiple HEBs and Wal-Marts your children will have  access to the Schertz/Cibolo School district.
